Package org.goplanit.osm.tags

Class OsmRoadModeTags

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.goplanit.osm.tags.OsmRoadModeTags
  • public class OsmRoadModeTags
extends Object
    Most OSM road based mode tags. Not included: water modes or very specialised modes. Based on list found on https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:access
    Author:
    markr
